🌤️ Weather App

A sleek and responsive || Weather App || that shows real-time weather information based on a city name using | HTML | CSS | JavaScript |. Powered by a public weather API (like OpenWeatherMap) for accurate results.

---

 📋 Features

- 🔍 Search weather by city
- 🌡️ Shows temperature, humidity, and weather conditions
- 📍 Optionally supports geolocation-based weather
- 💨 Wind speed display
- 🎨 Clean and responsive UI for all devices

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5 – Structure and layout  
- CSS3 – Styling and responsiveness  
- JavaScript (ES6)– API fetch and DOM manipulation  
- Weather API – Real-time weather data (OpenWeatherMap or similar)  
- Vercel – Deployment (optional)

